channel.title: Project Unknown - 317 - Soon to be Flawless
channel.description:
Greetings mopar users, today I am going to be sharing some of the knowledge on my new upcoming server: Project Unknown. Now of course the name will not be called Project Unknown but that is just to protect the name that I have in mind. Either way here are some details about it.
-Features- 98% Dueling - Needs a few small fixes. Minigames - Barrows - Pest Control All skills fully work, and I don't mean workarounds I mean the skills actually 100% work. Amazing Graphics for what it loads. A few custom items - for the people that love customs Player Owned Shops - 80% Working - Pretty much like the Grand Exchange I understand this has been done before.
This project has been in my care for about 13 months, have not really discussed it and it was just a thing to take my mind off school and work.
I will be posting photos in the near future you can expect a release date of around 8/15/2013 possibly sooner if you have any suggestions, questions, or thoughts feel free to send me a private message or post a comment.
